name: ElasticExportTreepodiaCOM
description: This plugin adds the format TreepodiaCOM to the Elastic Export.
author: plentymarkets GmbH
license: GNU AFFERO GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE Version 3, 19 November 2007

shortDescription.de: Die Integration des Datenformats Treepodia-Plugin ermöglicht die Artikeldatenübertragung zum Affiliate-Dienstleister Treepodia über den elastischen Export.
shortDescription.en: The integration of the data format Treepodia-Plugin enables the transfer of item data to the affiliate service provider Treepodia via the elastic export.
